# MotherDuck write-path cron lines — install per RUNBOOK-TUESDAY.md step (a.5). Staged 2026-07-12 (Lane B).
# These REPLACE the 09:00Z md_load_tables_v3 storefront refresh (comment it out, keep as fallback).

# publish committed nightly -> staging color -> validate/canaries -> atomic swap [2026-07-14]
*/30 6-15 * * * /usr/bin/flock -n /tmp/md_write_path.lock /root/md-migration/md_write_path.sh >> /root/md-migration/md_write_path.log 2>&1

# MotherDuck serving health + freshness watchdog (re-armed; was removed 07-10 to stop trial-credit burn)
*/15 * * * * /usr/bin/flock -n /tmp/md_watchdog.lock /usr/bin/python3 /root/md-migration/md_health_watchdog.py >> /root/md-migration/md_watchdog.log 2>&1
